# TrimX CLI Video Clipper

A Windows-native command-line tool for precise video clipping with intelligent lossless stream-copy and fallback re-encoding capabilities.

## Features

- Smart clipping strategy selection (auto/copy/reencode)
- GOP-spanning method for precise cuts
- Stream preservation (video, audio, subtitles)
- Multiple time format support
- Windows-optimized with long-path support

## Quick Start

```bash
# Clip a segment from a video file
clipper.exe clip --in "video.mov" --start 00:10:05.250 --end 00:12:40.000

# Inspect video file information
clipper.exe inspect --in "video.mov"

# Verify a clipped segment
clipper.exe verify --in "clipped.mov" --start 00:10:05.250 --end 00:12:40.000
```

